import { Box, Container, Paper, TextField, Typography } from "@mui/material";
import React from "react";

function SchoolForm(props) {
  return (
    <>
      <Container maxWidth="sm">
        <Paper
          variant="outlined"
          sx={{ my: { xs: 3, md: 6 }, p: { xs: 2, md: 3 } }}
        >
          <Box mt={2}>
            <Typography>Profit Calculator</Typography>
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="No. Of Students"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              required
            />
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              variant="outlined"
              label="Total Classes"
              required
              size="medium"
            ></TextField>
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              variant="outlined"
              label="Expense "
              required
              size="medium"
            ></TextField>
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              variant="outlined"
              label="Revenue"
              required
              size="medium"
            ></TextField>
          </Box>
        </Paper>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
}

export default SchoolForm;
